-- Czech Minister Backs Temelin Nuclear Plant Expansion, Pravo Says
-- B y   P e t e r   L a c a
-- 2013-02-19T07:21:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-19/czech-minister-backs-temelin-nuclear-plant-expansion-pravo-says.html
Expanding the Czech Republic’s
Temelin nuclear power plant is important for energy
independence,  Pravo  reported, citing Industry Minister Martin
Kuba.  CEZ AS, the Czech utility that operates Temelin, shouldn’t
receive permanent guarantees of electricity prices for Temelin
expansion, the newspaper reported, citing Kuba.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Peter Laca in Prague at 
 placa@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
